HEADWORD: Konze
<hw>Konze</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
large African antelope (<spn>Alcelaphus Lichtensteini</spn>), allied to
the hartbeest, but having shorter and flatter horns, and lacking a black
patch on the face.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

